publicationStmt.p: This data is extracted from the FnaG MSS Corpus, supplemented from other sources, and then re-used within the Corpus. It is for FnaG internal use only.

sourceDesc.p: The FnaG MSS Corpus has been transcribed from manuscripts and marked up with lexical and palaeographical data from various sources (e.g. eDIL). Transcriptions also have introductions, which are based on the relevant secondary literature and the editors' own observations.
